造成局势紧张<ref>{{Cite web|title=敦马：南海争端靠谈判 “大马不宜硬撼中国”|url=https://www.chinapress.com.my/20201229/%e6%95%a6%e9%a9%ac%ef%bc%9a%e5%8d%97%e6%b5%b7%e4%ba%89%e7%ab%af%e9%9d%a0%e8%b0%88%e5%88%a4-%e5%a4%a7%e9%a9%ac%e4%b8%8d%e5%ae%9c%e7%a1%ac%e6%92%bc%e4%b8%ad%e5%9b%bd/|accessdate=2020-12-30|work=中國報 China Press|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127072445/https://www.chinapress.com.my/20201229/%e6%95%a6%e9%a9%ac%ef%bc%9a%e5%8d%97%e6%b5%b7%e4%ba%89%e7%ab%af%e9%9d%a0%e8%b0%88%e5%88%a4-%e5%a4%a7%e9%a9%ac%e4%b8%8d%e5%ae%9c%e7%a1%ac%e6%92%bc%e4%b8%ad%e5%9b%bd/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

