2021-03-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>；同年8月9日，马哈迪与[[茜蒂哈斯玛|茜蒂哈斯玛]]应李显龙的邀请，出席新加坡国庆日及开埠200周年纪念游行<ref>{{Cite web|title=新国国庆日暨开埠200周年 敦马伉俪亲临见证|url=https://www.chinapress.com.my/20190809/%e6%96%b0%e5%9b%bd%e5%9b%bd%e5%ba%86%e6%97%a5%e6%9a%a8%e5%bc%80%e5%9f%a0200%e5%91%a8%e5%b9%b4-%e6%95%a6%e9%a9%ac%e4%bc%89%e4%bf%aa%e4%ba%b2%e4%b8%b4%e8%a7%81%e8%af%81/|accessdate=|date=2019-08-09|work=中國報 China Press|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207073028/https://www.chinapress.com.my/20190809/%E6%96%B0%E5%9B%BD%E5%9B%BD%E5%BA%86%E6%97%A5%E6%9A%A8%E5%BC%80%E5%9F%A0200%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4-%E6%95%A6%E9%A9%AC%E4%BC%89%E4%BF%AA%E4%BA%B2%E4%B8%B4%E8%A7%81%E8%AF%81/|archive-date=2021-02-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

