/www.sinchew.com.my/content/content_2283176.html|accessdate=2020-10-21|work=www.sinchew.com.my|archive-date=2021-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210426212307/https://www.sinchew.com.my/content/content_2283176.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=敦马：创斗士党为消除金钱政治|url=http://news.seehua.com/?p=596383|accessdate=2020-12-05|last=CYT|work=马来西亚诗华日报新闻网|archive-date=2021-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108201405/http://news.seehua.com/?p=596383|dead-url=no}}</ref>。11月21日，马哈迪在接受《[[日经亚洲评论|日经亚洲评论]]》专访时认为，斗士党在来届大选可成造王者<ref>{{Cite web|title=来届大选成第三势力 · 马哈迪：斗士党可成造王者|url=https://www.sinchew.com.my/content/content_2380475.html|accessdate=2020-11-21|work=www.sinchew.com.my|archive-date=2021-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210426213517/https://www.sinchew.com.my/content/content_2380475.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

