.com.my/20191119/%e6%95%a6%e9%a9%ac%e5%81%a5%e5%ba%b7%e6%97%a0%e7%a2%8d-%e6%9e%97%e5%86%a0%e8%8b%b1%ef%bc%9a%e5%9b%bd%e4%ba%ba%e4%b8%8d%e7%94%a8%e6%8b%85%e5%bf%83/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。首相官员之后也向媒体表示，马哈迪的确流鼻血，不过已经无碍及止血，同时回到[[布城首相署|布城首相暑]]继续办公<ref>{{Cite web|title=敦马流鼻血·官员强调健康无碍|url=https://www.sinchew.com.my/content/content_2149119.html|access-date=2021-05-02|work=www.sinchew.com.my|archive-date=2021-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210505042844/https://www.sinchew.com.my/content/content_2149119.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

